                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18410920-name-553" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18410920-name-553" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410920-name-553" type="surname" value="MERCER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18410920-name-553" type="given" value="ANN"></interp>ANN MERCER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am servant to Sir John Beresford, who lives in Har<lb></lb>ley-street, Cavendish-square. Between nine and ten o'clock in the morn<lb></lb>ing of the fifth of September, the prisoner came and swept the kitchen chimney, the housekeeper's room, and another—the plate was in the housekeeper's room—it was all right before—a policeman came on Tues<lb></lb>day morning, to know if we had lost any plate—we counted it, and missed this spoon.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
